{
  "id": "RAW_4d3a3c95",
  "title": "Vercel AI Gateway 现已支持团队级零数据保留（Zero Data Retention）和提示词训练控制",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/changelog/zero-data-retention-no-prompt-training-on-ai-gateway",
  "date": "2026-04-07 14:02:03",
  "author": "Matt Lenhard, Jeremy Philemon, Walter Korman, Jerilyn Zheng",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__XJFYTq__content\">\n   <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-between flex-initial w-full gap-4 pt-2\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-1.5 flex-initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900\">1<!-- --> min <!-- -->read</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6 flex-1 justify-start\"></div>\n    <time class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 order-2 md:order-3\" datetime=\"2026-04-06T00:00-07:00\">Apr 6, 2026</time>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">AI Gateway now supports Zero Data Retention (ZDR) at the team level, removing the need to configure opt-outs or reach agreements with each provider individually. It routes requests only to providers where ZDR agreements are in place, with support for Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, and many more models.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#team-wide-zdr\" id=\"team-wide-zdr\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" />\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a><b>Team-wide ZDR</b></h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Enable team-wide ZDR from the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fsettings&amp;title=AI+Gateway+Settings\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/d?to=%2F%5Bteam%5D%2F%7E%2Fai-gateway%2Fsettings&amp;title=AI+Gateway+Settings\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">AI Gateway Dashboard Settings</a> to enforce Zero Data Retention on every request your team makes, with no code changes required.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#request-level-zdr-&amp;-no-prompt-training\" id=\"request-level-zdr-&amp;-no-prompt-training\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" />\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a><b>Request-level ZDR &amp; No Prompt Training</b></h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">You can also configure ZDR and/or No Prompt Training on the request level by setting <code>zeroDataRetention: true</code> or <code>disallowPromptTraining: true</code> per request. Enabling Zero Data Retention automatically includes training opt-out, so there's no need to configure both separately.</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton code-block-module__NOThwW__copyFloatingButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-typescript code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L1\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">type</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> GatewayProviderOptions </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'@ai-sdk/gateway'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L2\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"> streamText </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'ai'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L3\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L4\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span><span class=\"token plain\"> result </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token function\">streamText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L5\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  model</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.6'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L6\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  prompt</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">'Summarize this internal document.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L7\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  providerOptions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L8\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    gateway</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L9\" data-highlighted=\"true\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      disallowPromptTraining</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L10\" data-highlighted=\"true\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">      zeroDataRetention</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L11\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">    </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token plain\"> satisfies GatewayProviderOptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L12\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">  </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C55491294-L13\" data-highlighted=\"false\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><b>Pricing</b></p>\n   <div class=\"scroller-module__6hSglq__overlayContainer text-module__qZtYrq__tableScroller scroller-module__6hSglq__isHorizontal\" data-geist-scroller=\"\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\">\n    <div class=\"scroller-module__6hSglq__scroller text-module__qZtYrq__scrollerContainer\" data-geist-scroller-container=\"\" data-overflow=\"x\">\n     <div class=\"\">\n      <table class=\"text-module__qZtYrq__table\">\n       <tbody>\n        <tr>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><b>Option</b></p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><b>Cost</b></p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><b>Availability</b></p>\n         </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Team-wide ZDR</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">$0.10 per 1,000 requests</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Pro and Enterprise</p>\n         </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Per-request ZDR</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Free</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Pro and Enterprise</p>\n         </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Disallow Prompt Training (per-request)</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Free</p>\n         </td>\n         <td>\n          <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">All users</p>\n         </td>\n        </tr>\n       </tbody>\n      </table>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Each response includes metadata showing which providers were considered and which were filtered out, giving you an audit trail of policy enforcement.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">These controls work with the AI SDK, Chat Completions API, Responses API, Anthropic Messages API, and OpenResponses API.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Read the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/capabilities/zdr\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/capabilities/zdr\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Zero Data Retention documentation</a> and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/capabilities/disallow-prompt-training\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/ai-gateway/capabilities/disallow-prompt-training\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">No Prompt Training documentation</a> for more details.</p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 引入了团队级和请求级的零数据保留（ZDR）及提示词训练控制功能，旨在简化跨多个 AI 提供商的数据隐私管理。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel AI Gateway 引入了团队级和请求级的零数据保留（ZDR）及提示词训练控制功能，旨在简化跨多个 AI 提供商的数据隐私管理。",
  "summary": "Vercel 更新了其 AI Gateway，以支持集中式的零数据保留（ZDR）和提示词训练控制。该功能允许团队通过自动将请求仅路由至具有有效 ZDR 协议（如 OpenAI、Anthropic 和 Google）的提供商，从而在所有请求中强制执行隐私策略。开发者可以通过仪表板全局启用这些控制（实现零代码部署），也可以通过 AI SDK 使用特定的请求级标志进行细粒度控制。虽然团队级 ZDR 是面向 Pro 和 Enterprise 用户的付费功能，但请求级控制是免费的，且所有响应都包含用于策略执行审计的元数据。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "跨多个 LLM 提供商的集中式零数据保留管理。",
      "explanation": "AI Gateway 通过自动将请求仅路由至具有有效 ZDR 协议的提供商，消除了与各提供商单独协商的复杂性，确保了隐私标准的一致性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过仪表板设置或代码级 SDK 标志实现双层强制执行。",
      "explanation": "团队可以通过 Vercel 仪表板选择零代码、团队级的强制执行，或者在应用程序代码中使用诸如 `zeroDataRetention: true` 的细粒度请求级控制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "集成的审计追踪和提示词训练选择退出机制。",
      "explanation": "启用 ZDR 会自动包含提示词训练的选择退出（opt-out），且每条响应都会提供详细说明哪些提供商被过滤的元数据，从而促进合规审计。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI Gateway 现已支持团队级的零数据保留（ZDR），无需再单独配置选择退出或与每个提供商达成协议。",
    "它仅将请求路由至已签署 ZDR 协议的提供商，并支持 Anthropic、OpenAI、Google 以及更多模型。",
    "启用零数据保留会自动包含训练选择退出，因此无需分别进行配置。",
    "每条响应都包含元数据，显示了哪些提供商被考虑在内，哪些被过滤掉，为您提供了策略执行的审计追踪。"
  ],
